  "description": "I wanna poke around at some stats about my files. Interestingly, as I\u0026rsquo;m writing this, it\u0026rsquo;ll produce new stats each time I update my Website. But I\u0026rsquo;m writing this on September 29th, 2025, and I started this research archive, with GnoponEmacs, on August 7th.\nFirst, I was curious: how many nodes do I have, what\u0026rsquo;s the mean number of links in each one, what\u0026rsquo;s the max links in one nodes, and how many are isolatd.\n",
